usdPppProfileAgent.name: usdPppProfileAgent

revisions.description: Added the authenticator virtual router object.
Added the IPCP netmask option object.
Added support for dynamic multi-link PPP (MLPPP) interfaces.
The initial release of this management information module.

usdPppProfileAgent.contactinfo: Unisphere Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@UnisphereNetworks.com
usdPppProfileAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the PPP Profile component of the SNMP agent in the Unisphere Routing Switch family of products.

usdPppProfileAgentV1.name: usdPppProfileAgentV1
usdPppProfileAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the PPP Profile component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the PPP Profile component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.0 through 3.2 system releases.
usdPppProfileAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPP Profile application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the dynamic multilink PPP object was added.

usdPppProfileAgentV2.name: usdPppProfileAgentV2
usdPppProfileAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the PPP Profile component of the Unisphere Routing Switch
        SNMP agent.  This version of the PPP Profile component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.3 system release.
usdPppProfileAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPP Profile application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the IPCP netmask option object was added.

usdPppProfileAgentV3.productrelease:

        SNMP agent.  This version of the PPP Profile component was supported in
        the Unisphere RX 3.4 and subsequent 3.x system releases.
usdPppProfileAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPP Profile application in the Unisphere Routing Switch. These capabilities became obsolete when the authenticator virtual router object was added.

usdPppProfileAgentV4.name: usdPppProfileAgentV4

usdPppProfileAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the PPP Profile application in the Unisphere Routing Switch.
